onFinishGeoCode

public boolean onFinishGeoCode(GeoCode geoCode)
Returns the reverse geocoding status: true - the request has been accepted, false - the request should be repeated.
Parameters:
geoCode - the GeoCode object which contains the result of reverse geocoding (the mailing address) or null if nothing has been found
Returns:
true if the request has been accepted, false - if the request should be repeated
